# Tools and MCPs for Unreal Engine 5.7

## Recommended MCPs (Model Context Protocol)

### 1. Unreal Engine MCP
**Repository**: https://github.com/flopperam/unreal-engine-mcp

**Description**: Allows controlling Unreal Engine 5.5+ via natural language commands.

**Features**:
- Create complex 3D worlds and architectural structures
- Build futuristic cities with skyscrapers
- Create complex mansions with multiple rooms
- Generate solvable mazes

**Requirements**:
- Unreal Engine 5.5+
- Python 3.12+
- MCP client (Cursor, Claude Desktop, Windsurf)

**Installation**:
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/flopperam/unreal-engine-mcp.git

# Follow installation instructions in README
```

